commits.content:
<project xmlns="http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0"
				 xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
				 xsi:schemaLocation="http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0 http://maven.apache.org/maven-v4_0_0.xsd">
	<modelVersion>4.0.0</modelVersion>
	<parent>
		<groupId>org.nuxeo</groupId>
		<artifactId>nuxeo-parent</artifactId>
		<version>2021.30.14</version>
	</parent>

	<groupId>amazon.devices</groupId>
	<artifactId>amazon-devices-parent</artifactId>
	<version>5.3.2-SNAPSHOT</version>
	<name>Amazon devices parent</name>
	<description>Amazon Devices DAM</description>
	<packaging>pom</packaging>

	<modules>
		<module>amazon-devices-core</module>
		<module>amazon-devices-keyword</module>
		<module>amazon-devices-package</module>
		<module>amazon-devices-web</module>
		<module>amazon-devices-portal</module>
	</modules>

	<properties>
		<nuxeo.skip.enforcer>true</nuxeo.skip.enforcer>
		<nuxeo.target.version>2021.*</nuxeo.target.version>
		<studio.project.version>feature/acxl-322-SNAPSHOT</studio.project.version>
	</properties>

	<scm/>
	<licenses/>
	<mailingLists/>
	<issueManagement/>
	<ciManagement/>
	<developers/>
	<distributionManagement/>

	<repositories>
		<repository>
			<id>nuxeo-studio</id>
			<url>https://connect.nuxeo.com/nuxeo/site/studio/maven/</url>
			<releases>
				<enabled>true</enabled>
			</releases>
			<snapshots>
				<updatePolicy>always</updatePolicy>
				<enabled>true</enabled>
			</snapshots>
		</repository>
		<repository>
			<id>maven-public</id>
			<url>https://packages.nuxeo.com/repository/maven-public/</url>
			<releases>
				<enabled>true</enabled>
			</releases>
			<snapshots>
				<updatePolicy>always</updatePolicy>
				<enabled>true</enabled>
			</snapshots>
		</repository>
		<repository>
			<id>maven-private</id>
			<url>https://packages.nuxeo.com/repository/maven-private/</url>
			<releases>
				<enabled>true</enabled>
			</releases>
			<snapshots>
				<updatePolicy>always</updatePolicy>
				<enabled>true</enabled>
			</snapshots>
		</repository>
	</repositories>

	<pluginRepositories>
		<pluginRepository>
			<id>maven-public</id>
			<url>https://packages.nuxeo.com/repository/maven-public/</url>
			<releases>
				<enabled>true</enabled>
			</releases>
			<snapshots>
				<enabled>false</enabled>
			</snapshots>
		</pluginRepository>
	</pluginRepositories>

	<dependencyManagement>
		<dependencies>
			<dependency>
				<groupId>amazon.devices</groupId>
				<artifactId>amazon-devices-core</artifactId>
				<version>${project.version}</version>
			</dependency>
			<dependency>
				<groupId>amazon.devices</groupId>
				<artifactId>amazon-devices-keyword</artifactId>
				<version>${project.version}</version>
			</dependency>
			<dependency>
				<groupId>amazon.devices</groupId>
				<artifactId>amazon-devices-package</artifactId>
				<version>${project.version}</version>
			</dependency>
			<dependency>
				<groupId>nuxeo-studio</groupId>
				<artifactId>amazon-devices-global-dam</artifactId>
				<version>${studio.project.version}</version>
			</dependency>
			<dependency>
				<groupId>amazon.devices</groupId>
				<artifactId>amazon-devices-web</artifactId>
				<version>${project.version}</version>
			</dependency>
			<dependency>
				<groupId>amazon.devices</groupId>
				<artifactId>amazon-devices-portal</artifactId>
				<version>${project.version}</version>
			</dependency>
		</dependencies>
	</dependencyManagement>

	<profiles>
		<profile>
			<id>release</id>
			<distributionManagement>
				<repository>
					<id>external-releases</id>
					<name>External Releases</name>
					<url>
						https://amazondevices-cicd-nexus.apps.prod.nuxeo.io/nexus/content/repositories/releases
					</url>
				</repository>
			</distributionManagement>
		</profile>
	</profiles>
</project>
